title: Let's Watch TV: Untold
description:
This week, Mama Fran decides to be an influencer and Joe gives her an ultimatum, before they get into the craziest show ever: Untold from Netflix. The first episode is about a former NFL football player who's career and life got turned upside down after getting catfished while in college.
